metours.com/downunderagainagainagain/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到。</p><p> Fred 再次......将在所有日期得到 Joy（匿名）的支持。</p><h3> <strong>Fred Again.. 的澳大利亚竞技场巡演日期是：</strong></h3><p><strong>行进</strong><br /><strong>04 – 罗德拉沃竞技场 – 墨尔本</strong><br /><strong>05 – 罗德拉沃竞技场 – 墨尔本</strong><br /><strong>06 – 罗德拉沃竞技场 – 墨尔本</strong><br /><strong>09 – 快闪店（地点待定） – 黄金海岸</strong><br /><strong>12 – 曲多斯银行竞技场 – 悉尼</strong><br /><strong>13 – 曲多斯班克竞技场 – 悉尼</strong><br /><strong>14 – 曲多斯班克竞技场 – 悉尼</strong></p><p>昨天（2 月 27 日），Fred 再次在标志性的悉尼歌剧院进行了最后一刻的演出，距离上午宣布演出不到 24 小时。虽然场馆可容纳 2,250 名观众，但仍有超过 125,000 人在网上排队，争取获得秘密演出的门票。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：stayinit" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/0DeGmYq33W6Svw1eTgnxDF?si=lRs6Y03yRFmDVTWEEh662w&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>在其他消息中，Fred 又与 Lil Yachty 于今天（2 月 28 日）发行了一首名为“stayinit”的新单曲。这位制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lil-yachty-perform-unreleased-track-stayinit-with-fred-again-3585644">此前曾于本月早些时候在纽约举行的一场惊喜演出中与说唱歌手一起表演了这首当时尚未发行的歌曲</a>。</p><p>弗雷德再次……将与拉娜·德尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">·雷 (Lana del Rey)</a>一起成为今年八月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-six-headliners-revealed-as-first-wave-of-line-up-announced-tickets-3548085">雷丁节周六的主角</a>。雷丁周六演出的门票<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-festival-2024-saturday-day-tickets-have-sold-out-3581366">已经售完</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fred-again-australia-arena-tour-surprise-sydney-opera-house-tickets-3593985">弗雷德再次宣布澳大利亚舞台巡演，在悉尼歌剧院演出后</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
阿黛尔因病暂停拉斯维加斯居住https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-pauses-las-vegas-residence-due-to-illness-3593857?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=adele-pauses-las-vegas-residence-due-疾病Surej SinghWed, 28 Feb 2024 01:57:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3593857 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “遵医嘱，我别无选择，只能好好休息”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-pauses-las-vegas-residence-due-to-illness-3593857">阿黛尔因病暂停拉斯维加斯居住的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/adele@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔</a>因病推迟了五周的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-extends-las-vegas-residency-with-32-more-shows-3518855">拉斯维加斯驻场演出</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/adele-30-album-review-dependable-pop-titan-finally-mixes-things-up-3096613">阿黛尔 – “30”专辑评论：可靠的流行巨星混合了一切</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（2月28日），这位受人尊敬的创作歌手在社交媒体上宣布，她必须“暂停”她长期驻场演出的五个周末的约会，并透露她在“最后一站结束时生病了”并一直贯穿我的休息时间。”</p><p>她接着解释说，她在生病期间继续参加了几场演出，但此后承受了后果：“在演出恢复之前，我还没有完全恢复健康，现在我又病了，不幸的是这对我的声音造成了影响。”</p><p> “所以，按照医生的嘱咐，我别无选择，只能好好休息。此赛段的剩余五个周末将被推迟到以后的日期。我们已经在制定细节，您将尽快收到信息，”阿黛尔写道。</p><p>阿黛尔还确认推迟的日期为3月1日、2日、8日、9日、15日、16日、22日、23日、29日和30日。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C33waGtPcfV/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><pat